MOST IMMEDIATE
No. 1/34/2/2005-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 8th November, 2005
17 Kartik, 1927(S).
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 7th November,
2005-
Shri K. Natwar Singh relinquished the charge of the office of the
Minister of External Affairs and assumed the charge of the office of
Minister Without Portfolio; and
i)
ii)
The Prime Minister assumed the charge of the office of the Minister
of External Affairs.
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 2301 5802
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to Deputy Chairman and Members of the
Planning Commission.
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary

Secretary to the President.
Secretary to the Vice-President.
(K.L. Sharma)
Deputy Secretary (Cabinet)
Copy also forwarded for information to :-
Principal Secretary to the Prime Minister.
(K.L. Sharma)
Deputy Secretary (Cabinet)
